      "span_text": "This is in concordance with a most recent study, in which HPV-positive head and neck cancer cell lines showed a considerable upregulation of miR-363 and an siRNA knockdown of HPV16 E6 was accompanied by a reduction of miR-363 levels [CITATION_1] ."
